-- Emaar, Countrywide to Expand Hamptons Operations in Europe, Africa, Asia
-- Shaji Mathew
-- 2010-06-17T10:47:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/emaar-countrywide-to-expand-hamptons-operations-in-europe-africa-asia.html

          
          
             Emaar Properties PJSC, the developer
of the world’s tallest tower in Dubai, reached an agreement with
Countrywide to expand the operations of Hamptons International.  
 Countrywide, a U.K. real estate and property services
company, will own the rights to operate Hamptons’s business in
the U.K., Europe and Asia, Emaar said in a statement to the
Dubai bourse today. Hamptons is a unit of Emaar.  
 Emaar will continue to operate Hamptons in the Middle East
and North Africa, according to the statement.  
